      <prop type="x-translation-ref">丰.1</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>子之丰兮，俟我乎巷兮。悔予不送兮。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>Full and good looking was the gentleman,
Who waited for me in the lane !
I repent that I did not go with him.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
