      <prop type="x-translation-ref">丰.2</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>子之昌兮，俟我乎堂兮。悔予不將兮。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>A splendid gentleman was he,
Who waited for me in the hall !
I regret that I did not accompany him.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
