      <prop type="x-translation-ref">丰.3</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>衣錦褧衣，裳錦褧裳。叔兮伯兮，駕予與行。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>Over my embroidered upper robe, I have put on a plain
single garment ;
Over my embroidered lower robe, I have done the same.
O Sir, O Sir,
Have your carriage ready for me to go with you.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
